         <div type="edition">
            <div type="textpart" subtype="inscription expanded title embedded" xml:lang="gez" xml:id="ExpandedTitle">
               <note>The following title is taken from <ref type="work" corresp="BNFet140"/>.</note>
               <ab>
                  በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መሓሪ፡ ወመስተሣህል፡
                  ወቦቱ፡ ረድኤትነ፤ ንቀድም፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወስነ፡ ስርሐቱ፡ በጽሒፈ፡ ዜና፡ ዘትበቍዕ፡ ለነፍስ፡ ወለሥጋ፡
                  ዘአምጽእዋ፡ እምሀገረ፡ ህንድ፡ እስከ፡ ቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ ወጸሐፋ፡ ፩፡ መነኮስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ዘእምጌቴሴማኒ፡ ዘስሙ፡ ዮሐንስ፡
                  በረከተ፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ወትንብልናሁ፡ ተሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ <persName ref="PRS5617IyasuII">
                     <certainty locus="value" match=".../@ref" cert="unknown"/>ኢያሱ፡</persName>
                  ወምስለ፡ ፍቁሩ፡ <persName role="owner" ref="PRS11290Ebeselom">ኤቤሴሎም፡</persName> ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡
                  አሜን።
               </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="inscription expanded title embedded" xml:lang="en" corresp="#ExpandedTitle">
               <note>The following title is taken from <ref type="work" corresp="BNFet140"/>.</note>
               <ab>
                  In the name of God, the merciful and compassionate, in whom our aid is,
                  we begin with the help of God and with his graceful generosity with the writing of a profitable story for the soul and body, which was brought from India to Jerusalem and
                  was written by a holy monk from Gethsemane, by the name of Yoḥannǝs.
                  May the blessing of his prayer and intercession be with our king <persName ref="PRS5617IyasuII">ʾIyāsu</persName>
                  and his beloved <persName ref="PRS11290Ebeselom">ʾEbeselom</persName>.
               </ab>
            </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
               <ab>
                  ይቤ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ እስመ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ እለ፡ ይገብሩ፡ ግብረ፡ መንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ እሙንቱ፡ ውሉደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡
               </ab>
            </div>
